00:20:34.971 --> 00:20:38.997
Because the truth is, I look a lot like I've always looked.

00:20:40.318 --> 00:20:42.721
I wasn't seeing a new reflection in the mirror.

00:20:44.123 --> 00:20:46.546
It was God who put that thought in my mind.

00:20:47.298 --> 00:20:55.812
And I was finally for the first time seeing myself like he sees me and I loved it.

00:20:57.514 --> 00:21:01.861
I mean I loved me because he loves me.

00:21:04.425 --> 00:21:07.170
Ramon realized he wasn't alone.

00:21:07.210 --> 00:21:12.338
And so he wasn't ashamed and he wasn't lost and he wasn't lonely.

00:21:12.770 --> 00:21:20.701
Ramon realized he wanted to live, that he had an origin, a conflict and resolution that made all the good in his life worth savoring and all the bad worth facing.

00:21:21.022 --> 00:21:25.368
He realized that he had not found home, but that home had found him.

00:21:25.408 --> 00:21:41.490
He was just shaving, just getting ready for work one morning like any other morning when the whisper we call Christmas said something to him that sounded a lot like, you are my son.

00:21:42.498 --> 00:21:45.743
whom I love with you, I'm well pleased.

00:21:46.684 --> 00:21:50.870
Belief requires some crack within me where love can get in.

00:21:52.513 --> 00:21:58.522
And I just wonder if that might be happening to a person or two right now.

00:22:00.565 --> 00:22:05.212
If there's some crack within you where love is able to get in.

00:22:05.232 --> 00:22:12.082
And if it is, you should know that you can push that away if you want.

00:22:13.890 --> 00:22:18.376
Sentiment or cynicism is every bit as on the table as love.

00:22:20.339 --> 00:22:30.152
But then you'd walk out of this place just like you came in, swimming through a sea of strangers, surrounded, but alone.

00:22:31.454 --> 00:22:37.362
Or I guess you could walk out just the same in the eyes of everybody else, only within you you would finally be home.

00:22:38.434 --> 00:22:47.444
because the life of Jesus in the celebration of Christmas is God's most personal declaration that He won't wait for you to come home.

00:22:48.025 --> 00:22:51.109
Home is what He has brought to you.

00:22:51.949 --> 00:22:58.237
Let's stand and we'll pray together.

